&lt;p>First of all, I didn&amp;rsquo;t &lt;strong>make&lt;/strong> this website.&lt;br>
It&amp;rsquo;s a fork of the relatively popular &lt;a href="https://github.com/kaiiiz/hugo-theme-monochrome/">hugo-monochrome&lt;/a>
theme that I&amp;rsquo;m hacking on. It&amp;rsquo;s a really well designed theme that has all the features I need for a
simple blog/projects/misc website. I&amp;rsquo;m hosting it on Github Pages because it&amp;rsquo;s free and convenient.
I&amp;rsquo;m not planning on making posts daily, weekly or even monthly. This website is for writing down my
thoughts, posting interesting stuff that I learned and maybe cringy attempts at trying to teach
people how to do various stuff.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>